#

Grilled Vegetable Borscht

45 min
$8
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern EuropeanUkrainian

Course:

SoupMain Course

Tags:

EasyHealthySoupVegetarian

Description

A vibrant and healthy twist on the traditional borscht, featuring grilled vegetables for a smoky flavor.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • carrots: 1 large, sliced
  • bell pepper: 1, diced
  • zucchini: 1 medium, sliced
  • onion: 1 small, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh dill: for garnish
